high_descs: Walk straight to the window on the far wall and turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn right for ten steps and turn left to face the microwave oven.
Open the door of the microwave, put the potato in the center of the black dish, shut the door, turn on the oven for a few seconds, open the door and take the potato out then shut the door again.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right, walk over to the white table.
Put the potato on the table to the right of the handle of the knife, on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the white table.

high_descs: Walk across the room, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the potato off of the counter.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn left to face the microwave.
Heat up the potato in the microwave for a couple seconds and then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the white table.
Put the heated potato on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on a white table.

high_descs: walk to face counter above dishwasher
heat and remove potato from microwave
put potato inside bowl on table
anns.task_desc: put heated potato inside bowl on table
